Package com.github.robtimus.net.ip

Contains utility classes for working with IP addresses.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IPRange<IP extends IPAddress<IP>>
    Represents a range of consecutive IP addresses.
    IPv4Range
    Represents a range of consecutive IPv4 addresses.
    IPv6Range
    Represents a range of consecutive IPv6 addresses.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractIPRange<IP extends IPAddress<IP>>
    A skeleton implementation of the IPRange interface.
    AbstractIPv4Range
    A skeleton implementation of the IPRange interface for IPv4 addresses.
    AbstractIPv6Range
    A skeleton implementation of the IPRange interface for IPv6 addresses.
    IPAddress<IP extends IPAddress<IP>>
    Represents an IP address.
    IPAddressFormatter<IP extends IPAddress<?>>
    Formatter for printing and parsing IP addresses.
    IPAddressFormatter.Builder<IP extends IPAddress<?>>
    A builder for formatters for printing and parsing IP addresses.
    IPRangeSpliterator<IP extends IPAddress<IP>>
    A spliterator for IP ranges.
    IPv4Address
    Represents an IPv4 address.
    IPv4RangeSpliterator
    A spliterator for IPv4 ranges.
    IPv4Subnet
    Represents a subnet of IPv4 addresses.
    IPv6Address
    Represents an IPv6 address.
    IPv6RangeSpliterator
    A spliterator for IPv6 ranges.
    IPv6Subnet
    Represents a subnet of IPv6 addresses.
    Subnet<IP extends IPAddress<IP>>
    Represents a subnet of IP addresses.
